"""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
"   General
"""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""

" Search
set hlsearch
set ignorecase
set smartcase

" Use the system pasteboard
set clipboard=unnamed

" Jump to definition more easily
nmap <C-j> <C-]>

" Comment code easily
nmap gcc :xcmenucmd Toggle Comments<CR>

" Insert a line below current line
nmap <space>ij o<ESC>k
" Insert a line above the current line
nmap <space>ik O<ESC>j


""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
"   SpaceCODE
"
" I use Spacemacs, thus, spacebar is my leader
" However, that also means that I have some ingrained commands in my hands.
" These will be respected, even if in Xcode, they don't make exact sense
""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""

" Window management
nmap <space>wv <C-w>v
nmap <space>ws <C-w>s
nmap <space>wd <C-w>c
nmap <space>wo :xcmenucmd Show Standard Editor<CR>
nmap <space>wg :xcmenucmd Show Version Editor<CR>

" Window navigation
nmap <space>wh <C-w>h
nmap <space>wl <C-w>l
nmap <space>wj <C-w>j
nmap <space>wk <C-w>k

" File commands
nmap <space>fs :xcmenucmd Save<CR>

" Search commands
nmap <space>pf :xcmenucmd Open Quickly...<CR>
nmap <space>/ :xcmenucmd Open Quickly...<CR>
nmap <space>sup viw:xccmd findSelectedTextInWorkspace<CR>

" Compilation commands
nmap <space>cC :xcmenucmd Run<CR>
nmap <space>cr :xcmenucmd Run<CR>
nmap <space>ct :xcmenucmd Test<CR>
nmap <space>cb :xcmenucmd Bulid<CR>
nmap <space>cc :xcmenucmd Clean Build Folder<CR>

" Breakpoints
nmap <space>tb :xcmenucmd toggleBreakpointAtCurrentLine<CR>
